<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="individual-adj">individual <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɪndɪ'vɪdʒuəl/    美 /ˌɪndɪ'vɪdʒuəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>单独的；个人的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Each individual</strong> leaf on the tree is different.
树上的每片叶子都不相同。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is difficult for a teacher to give individual attention to children in a large class.
在人数多的班上教师很难照顾到每个孩子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>独特的；与众不同的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's got a very individual way of dressing.
她穿衣非常有个性。</p></div></div>